{"tid":1451680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係唔撚明2，明明84萬人就塞爆地鐵，而加要百萬人去停機場，明知有鬼搞事，明知機場高火力，做咩姐?","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:25:04.000Z","uid":190086,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3134c670b57d5166367e60533ace4439d1cb7dc3","tid":1451680,"uid":190086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:02:16.000Z","msg":"一車地鐵坐2800人，1分鐘一班要168,000人<br />\n目標塞5條線先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">840,000</span></span><br />\n仲係計緊大家咁乖唔拖喼，車門次次山到先要840,000人 <br />\n如果個個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拖喼加有人衝車門條數直接除2<br />\n先要420,000</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做唔到咪先去機場囉，總至目標set係有420,000勇武+和理非既人係去做，<br />\n唔會話驚阻人翻工咩咩柒柒，你日日塞爆都得啦<br />\n老老實實，到時都唔洗理民意，淨坐唔搞事邊個可以郁你"},{"pid":"07effab1bd6a2acac928420b319072581f8b2ce3","tid":1451680,"uid":190086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:03:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"332ba750fa8d24f3eb16c581c5a35c1f3e6be259","tid":1451680,"uid":190086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:05:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8609134d364be37f82b0734365c3421063c5044","tid":1451680,"uid":190086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:06:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cef4c1296cbee46e079bce6e826ed4f8badd0394","tid":1451680,"uid":190086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18d872b1f856389ebb84c9774db3d1a5d1e890ae","tid":1451680,"uid":103476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:06:15.000Z","msg":"借位，幫手推<br />\n<br />\n［幫手置頂］即學如何對付癲狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451659</a>"},{"pid":"1e71cb663bd4a8c4f2e859eef65384633ca7e676","tid":1451680,"uid":256857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:06:17.000Z","msg":"理性討論<br />\n我覺得香港人返工意慾太強<br />\n搭唔到地鐵就會去搭巴士 <br />\n再唔係就的士 塞地鐵作用有限<br />\n反而機場係出入香港同外地嘅唯一途徑<br />\n搞機場個威力會唔會大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb5e3756b27b34507a1d3875b896b1d186f761d","tid":1451680,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:07:16.000Z","msg":"機場最安全"},{"pid":"562759080828f4210cbba8728eb1f5deaabbf706","tid":1451680,"uid":287387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:07:38.000Z","msg":"機場政府命脈，睇佢次次冷處理就知"},{"pid":"446aedc22ff7029a14e3209853492467cb4d3219","tid":1451680,"uid":15477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:39.000Z","msg":"你太高估港豬<br />\n呢啲不合作運動唔會有咁多人同你出嚟"},{"pid":"af20d3f25d0a47e831721929ef203895928d0477","tid":1451680,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"唔好再搞地鐵 <br />\n香港人無得番工仲大獲過黑警開真槍"},{"pid":"53bbe45988b982a163a94021d9bb43f465c5d660","tid":1451680,"uid":271485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:12:06.000Z","msg":"開始有人洗版話唔好搞機場<br />\n唔好搞禁區<br />\n同五年前金紫荊一樣<br />\n亦同今年200萬人鳩行一樣<br />\n即係方响正確<br />\n爭在啲豬會唔會同以往一樣"},{"pid":"625d68c28ef1548bb72ce8b1a8aa03c507a2fbf3","tid":1451680,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:15:35.000Z","msg":"有巴打諗到一個毒計, 一人可以癱瘓MTR一輛列車<br />\n大家有看過嗎?"},{"pid":"6c4a7acbbadf72d34531bc0edc606b4398c6588e","tid":1451680,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:15.000Z","msg":"#1Kkkkkw<br />\n<br />\n&bull;11m<br />\n<br />\n完全封鎖"},{"pid":"b378473744d438ca00e02f29e7d1a55629f7799d","tid":1451680,"uid":37408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:17:20.000Z","msg":"一百萬人由香港唔同位置湧入機場<br />\n全香港都癱啦"},{"pid":"38058d8eb2a8223bbdf40974b8f18ac5a338b178","tid":1451680,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:18:23.000Z","msg":"機場安全過地鐵 <br />\n<br />\n不推文"},{"pid":"80361618e2